data.description:
Super cute bungalow ready for you to move in. 
Main level living 2 bedroom and 1 full bath home with lots of character.  Walk in from the covered/rocking chair front porch to the living room with decorative fireplace.  Eat-in kitchen and laundry on the enclosed back porch. 
Outbuildings will be removed and do not convey with the home. 
Acreage: .27
Schools: Longview, Grandview, Hickory High
